NG0622:1: rtag tu dri ma med pa thugs rje'i shugs las byung *//
NG0622:2: smon lam 'grub pa 'gag pa med pa'i chos nyid can //
NG0622:3: 'gro ba'i don grub rab tu brtson pa mtha' yas pa //
NG0622:4: thugs rje chen po'i bdag nyid rtag tu rnam par snang *//
NG0622:5: tshad med tshad dang bral ba shin tu rdzogs pa yi //
NG0622:6: bde bar gshegs pa'i go 'phang dam pa shin tu mnyes gyur kyang *//
NG0622:7: khams gsum rnams la dngos grub mchog stsol mdzad pa yi //
NG0622:8: thugs rje'i spyod pa mi g.yo 'gag par yang mi 'gyur //
NG0622:9: e ma ho shin tu bzang po'i chos nyid mchog dang ldan //
NG0622:10: mchog sbyin rnams kyi nang na go 'phang mchog mnyes pas //
NG0622:11: khams gsum kun la dngos grub mchog stsol mdzad pa yi //
NG0622:12: mgon po dus gsum sgrib pa med par rab mkhyen pa //
NG0622:13: dam tshig mchog gsum dngos grub dam pa bdag la stsol //
NG0622:15: de nas de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis shin
NG0622:16: tu gdug pa 'dul ba'i tshogs rnams la yon tan
NG0622:18: sgeg pa dpa' ba 'jig su rungs pa dang *//
NG0622:19: rgod dang gshe dang rngams pa'i nga ro dang *//
NG0622:20: snying rje rngam dang ngo mtshar chen po dang *//
NG0622:21: sku yi dngos po shin tu 'gyur ba'i gar //
NG0622:22: dur khrod rus pa'i rgyan rnams rab tu mdzad //
NG0622:23: theg mchog glang chen ko ba brjid dang ldan //
NG0622:24: thabs mkhas zhing chen pags pa mdzes pa'i rgyan //
NG0622:25: 'jo sgeg stag gi pags pa chos nyid rgyan //
NG0622:26: rak+ta thal chen zhag gi mi srin dbang du sdud //
NG0622:27: bdud dang sren po tshar gcod ru tra sgrol //
NG0622:28: dpa' rtags mtshon cha thabs kyi ye shes me //
NG0622:29: bdud kyi bdud 'joms bdud dpung thal bar rlog /
NG0622:30: drag po drag chen drag rgyal he ru ka /
NG0622:31: mtshan dpes rgyan ldan 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa //
NG0622:32: sku yi gar mdzad gsang sgor 'gro ba 'jug / tug chom 'brug sgra stang khams bgegs sa sgrogs //
NG0622:33: gad rgyangs gad mos gsang ba'i bshugs glu len //
NG0622:34: rtag chad mu stegs 'gog pa nyan thos bu //
NG0622:35: dman pa'i theg pa log lta 'byung po 'dul //
NG0622:36: seng ge'i nga ros gcan gzan gdug pa 'dul //
NG0622:37: tshangs pa'i dbyangs kyis skal ldan rnal 'byor skyong *//
NG0622:38: chos 'chad log lta tshar gcod bdud dregs 'dul //
NG0622:39: ngan song stongs mdzad thar pa'i lam la 'god //
NG0622:40: thugs rjes 'dren pa snying rje'i rgyun thag can //
NG0622:41: smon 'jug sems lnga bskyed cing nyon mongs 'dul //
NG0622:42: zhi des byams pa'i gsang ba kun la sgrogs //
NG0622:43: 'dul sprul ma nges nges pa'i skur ston cing *//
NG0622:44: ngo mtshar gzugs snang khang stong nam mkha'i 'ja' //
NG0622:45: sems can don mdzad 'dul sgo nyon mongs zhi //
NG0622:46: rig pa'i rgyal po bla med he ru ka / rig 'dzin rnal 'byor dngos grub mchog stsol mdzad //
NG0622:47: rnam dag sku lnga 'jigs pas nam mkha' 'dra //
NG0622:48: sha dang khrag med stong pa ye shes @#//
NG0622:50: gdos bcas dug 'joms dpa' bo 'jigs pa bral //
NG0622:51: sku gsung lhun grub brdal ba thig le che //
NG0622:52: snang stong dbyer med shes rab thabs ldan sku //
NG0622:53: 'khor dang mya ngan 'das pa rdzogs par rol //
NG0622:54: rgyud kyi rgyal po chen po sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor las //
NG0622:55: yon tan yongs su brjod pa'i le'u ste rtog pa
NG0622:56: bcu pa'o // // de nas de bzhin gshegs pa
NG0622:57: sras sangs rgyas byang chub skal ldan ma dang */
NG0622:69: sangs rgyas byang chub ma dang */
NG0622:83: sna tshogs ba dan 'dzin ma dang */
NG0622:96: gtum pa'i dbang phyug ma dang */
NG0622:100: sna tshogs pad+ma rgya gram ma dang */
NG0622:101: sna tshogs rdo rje ma dang */
NG0622:122: gzhan yang dpa' bo thams cad dang *//
NG0622:125: byang chub sems dpa'i rigs su gyur pa thams cad dang */
NG0622:126: gsang ba'i rigs su gyur pa thams cad kyis //
NG0622:127: mnyes pa chen po'i mchod pas mchod do //
NG0622:128: rtog pa'i rgyal po nyid la rjes su yi rang bar mdzad pa'i phyir /
NG0622:138: spro ba de nyid dbyer med par gyur te /
NG0622:140: lam spros pa'i rgyud du ston to //
NG0622:141: 'bras bu yongs su 'dus pa'i rgyud du ston to //
NG0622:142: mang du bskyed pa'i rgyud du bstan to //
NG0622:143: nyung du sdud pa'i rgyud du bstan to //
NG0622:144: yongs su 'dus pa rtsa bar bstan to //
NG0622:146: bkod pa bshad par bstan to //
NG0622:147: lkog tu gyur par ston pa kha skong bstan to //
NG0622:148: mdud pa dgrol bar dka' ba gcod par bstan to //
NG0622:149: des de bzhin du gsungs so //
NG0622:150: de nas de bzhin du mkhyen to //
NG0622:151: de rnams de bzhin du yi rang bar gyur to //
NG0622:153: de nyid de bzhin du gyur to //
NG0622:154: de nyid de bzhin sdud do //
NG0622:155: de nyid de bzhin bsdus nas de bzhin du gsungs so //
NG0622:161: rgyud kyi rgyal po sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor las /

NG0622:165: sangs rgyas thams cad dang mnyam par sbyor ba zhes bya ba /
NG0622:166: mkha' 'gro sgyu ma bde mchog / dus gsum sangs
NG0622:167: rgyas thams cad kyi sku 'dus pa chen po'i rang
NG0622:168: bzhin sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor gyi rgyud rdzogs so //
